<template>
    <v-container>
        <v-row>
            <v-col>
                <v-card>
                    <v-card-title>
                        주문목록
                    </v-card-title>
                    <v-card-text>
                        v-dat
                        :headers="tableHeader"
                        :items="orderList"
                        show-expend
                    </v-card-text>
                </v-card>
            </v-col>
        </v-row>
    </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default{
    data(){
        tableHeader:[{title:"ID",key:"id"},{title:"회원이름",key:"member.name"},{title:"회원email",key:"member.email"}]
        orderList:{}
    },
    async created(){
        try{
            const response = await axios.get(`${process.env.VUE_APP_API_BASE_URL}/orderling/list`);
            this.orderList = response.data.result;
        }catch(e){
            console.log(e);
        }
    }

}
</script>
